        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nHi,\n\nI have now made changes for AAI-2617 to remove the search guard from the setup.\nThis has been tested by in my local lab (note that in my lab- due to test certificate issue, I had to use elalto branch pom.xml to build my search data image to do end to end testing but all code base was from master branch only , hence I presume it should be fine).\n\nFyi, test steps done by me via postman to search data MS:\n1. Create a new index.\n2. Add new document.\n3. Query the document.\nExpect successful responses.\n\n\nI would be thankful to you if you could please review and approve.\n\nRegards,\nRajeev",
